liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: No upsets here, the Dutch do it without TOO much trouble against South Africa. Banyana Banyana deserve a lot of credit for the way they kept coming at the Netherlands, especially for a 15-minute period at the end of the first half when they created chance after chance through Thembi Kgatlana (what a shame to see her go home). Roord and Beerensteyn the goalscorers for the Netherlands - who now face Spain in the quarter-finals. What a tantilising battle that will be. Don't ask me who the favourite is.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: FULL-TIME: Netherlands 2 - 0 South Africa

children.content: No upsets here, the Dutch do it without TOO much trouble against South Africa.

Banyana Banyana deserve a lot of credit for the way they kept coming at the Netherlands, especially for a 15-minute period at the end of the first half when they created chance after chance through Thembi Kgatlana (what a shame to see her go home).
Roord and Beerensteyn the goalscorers for the Netherlands - who now face Spain in the quarter-finals. What a tantilising battle that will be. Don't ask me who the favourite is.

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Lineth Beerensteyn sets off down the left and from a tight angle unleashes a shot. It should have been comfortably saved by Swart but it slips through her hands and into the net. South Africa up against it now. Just a shame it had to happen that way.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: 68' GOAAAAL NETHERLANDS - Goalkeeping howler!

children.content: Lineth Beerensteyn sets off down the left and from a tight angle unleashes a shot. It should have been comfortably saved by Swart but it slips through her hands and into the net.
South Africa up against it now. Just a shame it had to happen that way.
